The Human Factor 2018
https://www.proofpoint.com/sites/default/files/gtd-pfpt-us-wp-human-factor-report-2018-180425.pdf
"Fake browser and plugin updates appeared in massive malvertising campaigns affecting millions of users. As many as 95% of observed web-based attacks like these, including those involving exploit kits, incorporated social engineering to trick users into installing malware rather than relying on exploits with short shelf lives. "
